marketing: Shell EcoSafe EAL 46 is a high-performance, environmentally acceptable hydraulic fluid. Shell EcoSafe EAL 46 is produced from biodegradable base stocks and can replace traditional mineral oil hydraulic fluid in in systems with little to no equipment modifications and minimal downtime to provide outstanding performance across a wide range of conditions. Shell EcoSafe EAL 46 fluids can be relied on to provide optimal performance in a wide range of outdoor climates, across a wide temperature operating window.
